  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677770/extras/0d1484544b367b4e819fe6cd3561e2d4.poster.avif?t=1758227116\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677770/extras/0d1484544b367b4e819fe6cd3561e2d4.webm?t=1758227116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677770/extras/0d1484544b367b4e819fe6cd3561e2d4.mp4?t=1758227116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677770/extras/9942302288c1c9079c170ec65a507ff3.avif?t=1758227116\" width=606 height=168 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677770/extras/5f49e929bebf2362f965adcc885ef81a.avif?t=1758227116\" width=600 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Step into the shoes of an 18th century detective and uncover the mystery behind twelve strange deaths spanning 50 years, all somehow connected. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Unmask the true killers in this sprawling narrative and discover their devious motives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677770/extras/adab6ad912e63587f3e0c9a62c701c12.poster.avif?t=1758227116\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677770/extras/adab6ad912e63587f3e0c9a62c701c12.webm?t=1758227116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677770/extras/e3f3b2b33013012284750e7d7f863d31.avif?t=1758227116\" width=600 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Observe closely and reconstruct each scene of death. Your skills of deduction can identify each suspect, motive and murder weapon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677770/extras/cf40c5d6e07c814c2301c27a87093b73.poster.avif?t=1758227116\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677770/extras/cf40c5d6e07c814c2301c27a87093b73.webm?t=1758227116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677770/extras/738251f8e253ed35b502b0862a2f89e7.avif?t=1758227116\" width=600 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Reveal the true nature of the mysterious Golden Idol and those who covet it. Follow the journey of a cursed aristocratic family as you untangle a web of deceit and villainy in your hunt for the truth behind this dark conspiracy.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677770/extras/0d1484544b367b4e819fe6cd3561e2d4.poster.avif?t=1758227116\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677770/extras/0d1484544b367b4e819fe6cd3561e2d4.webm?t=1758227116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677770/extras/0d1484544b367b4e819fe6cd3561e2d4.mp4?t=1758227116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677770/extras/9942302288c1c9079c170ec65a507ff3.avif?t=1758227116\" width=606 height=168 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677770/extras/5f49e929bebf2362f965adcc885ef81a.avif?t=1758227116\" width=600 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Step into the shoes of an 18th century detective and uncover the mystery behind twelve strange deaths spanning 50 years, all somehow connected. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Unmask the true killers in this sprawling narrative and discover their devious motives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677770/extras/adab6ad912e63587f3e0c9a62c701c12.poster.avif?t=1758227116\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677770/extras/adab6ad912e63587f3e0c9a62c701c12.webm?t=1758227116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677770/extras/e3f3b2b33013012284750e7d7f863d31.avif?t=1758227116\" width=600 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Observe closely and reconstruct each scene of death. Your skills of deduction can identify each suspect, motive and murder weapon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677770/extras/cf40c5d6e07c814c2301c27a87093b73.poster.avif?t=1758227116\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677770/extras/cf40c5d6e07c814c2301c27a87093b73.webm?t=1758227116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677770/extras/738251f8e253ed35b502b0862a2f89e7.avif?t=1758227116\" width=600 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Reveal the true nature of the mysterious Golden Idol and those who covet it. Follow the journey of a cursed aristocratic family as you untangle a web of deceit and villainy in your hunt for the truth behind this dark conspiracy.</p>",
